# Regenerate the README demo:  cd assets && vhs demo.tape

Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 920
Set Height 540
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 70ms
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type 'syncthis() { bash ./demo.sh; }; clear'
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show

Type "syncthis run"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
